<p>Renders a <code>&lt;td&gt;</code>. Add
  <code>classes: "table-data-numeric"</code> for right-aligned
  tabular numbers. For complex tables, link the cell to header
  cells via <code>headers</code>. See the
  <a href="/components/table/">Table demo</a> for the composed
  example.</p>
